verbose_text: The reduced concentration of myoglobin and increased concentration of collagen in the SOL muscle (XREF_FIG), the decreased levels of actinin and increased concentration of phosphoglycerate kinase in EDL muscle (XREF_FIG), the lower levels of parvalbumin and higher levels of serpina in the FDB muscle (XREF_FIG) and the reduced expression of parvalbumin and increased concentration of alphaB-crystallin in the INT muscle (XREF_FIG) was verified by immunoblot analysis.
